OL,3,CGovernment appoints commissioners to
OL,4,Crun 'bankrupt' Nottingham City Council
OL,6,FThe Government has appointed
OL,7,Fcommissioners to run Nottingham City
OL,8,FCouncil, after the authority
OL,10,FThe Labour-run authority issued a
OL,11,Fsection 114 notice on 29 November
OL,12,F2023, after revealing it was set for a
OL,13,F#23million overspend before the end of
OL,14,Fthe financial year.
OL,16,FA Government-appointed board has
OL,17,Foverseen changes at the council since
OL,18,Fthe collapse of council firm Robin
OL,19,FHood Energy in 2020, which cost the
OL,20,Ftaxpayer an estimated #38million.
