OL,3,CGovernment appoints commissioners to
OL,4,Crun 'bankrupt' Nottingham City Council
OL,6,FHe said: "The Secretary of State is
OL,7,Fsatisfied that Nottingham City Council
OL,8,Fis continuing to fail to comply with
OL,9,Fits Best Value Duty, and that the
OL,10,Fnecessary improvements are still not
OL,11,Fbeing made quickly enough.
OL,13,F"I am today confirming that
OL,14,Fcommissioners have been appointed to
OL,15,FNottingham City Council and new
OL,16,Fdirections have been issued."
