OL,3,CGovernment appoints commissioners to
OL,4,Crun 'bankrupt' Nottingham City Council
OL,6,FThe commissioners have been appointed
OL,7,Ffor two years and will work alongside
OL,8,Fthe existing structure of the council,
OL,9,Fwith all officers, elected officials
OL,10,Fand the leader, David Mellen,
OL,11,Fremaining in place.
OL,13,FA report discussed at an Executive
OL,14,FBoard meeting in November 2023
OL,15,Fhighlighted that a significant gap
OL,16,Fremained in the authority's budget,
OL,17,Fdue to issues including an increased
OL,18,Fdemand for children's and adults'
OL,19,Fsocial care, a rising number of rough
OL,20,Fsleepers and the impact of inflation.
