OL,6,FThe council said it has "sufficient
OL,7,Ffinancial resources to meet all of its
OL,8,Fcurrent obligations, to continue to
OL,9,Fpay staff, suppliers and grant
OL,10,Frecipients in this year."
OL,12,FAn extensive budget savings package
OL,13,Fwhich the council says will have a
OL,14,Fsignificant impact on local services,
OL,15,Fis due to be decided on by councillors
OL,16,Fat a meeting on 4 March 2024.
