OL,3,CGovernment appoints commissioners to
OL,4,Crun 'bankrupt' Nottingham City Council
OL,6,FIn response to the Government
OL,7,Fappointments, Councillor David Mellen,
OL,8,FLeader of the Council, said: "Our
OL,9,Fpreferred option was to continue to
OL,10,Fwork with the Improvement and
OL,11,FAssurance Board which has been
OL,12,Foverseeing improvements at the council
OL,13,Fsince 2021.
OL,15,F"We feel that significant progress was
OL,16,Fbeing made across the council.
OL,17,FHowever, we are committed to working
OL,18,Fconstructively and collaboratively
OL,19,Fwith the Commissioners to tackle
OL,20,FNottingham's current challenges."
