OL,6,FMel Barrett, the council's Chief
OL,7,FExecutive, said: "The council is
OL,8,Fcommitted to working in collaboration
OL,9,Fwith the Commissioners to continue our
OL,10,Fimprovement journey at pace, reshaping
OL,11,Fthe organisation to put the authority
OL,12,Fon a stable financial footing, while
OL,13,Fdelivering essential services for
OL,14,FNottingham residents within the
OL,15,Fresources that we have.
